nodes.text: The master of the wilwog Itipiniwi brought sexes to the Annual Mid-Rim Domesticated Sub-Sentient Show. Itipiniwi was awarded "Best in Show," which caused her owner to become excited and produce noise, which Itipiniwi imitated. The noise caused Boshuda, another pet at the show, to become agitated and eat Itipiniwi.
